workouts.introText:
Your legs are the foundation for your full-body strength â€“ so let's give them a full-on workout.


Chris and Luke have remixed your routine to keep you making progress, so start with the tutorial, then make sure you're upping your weight when you're ready.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: While your weight is on your front leg, your back leg will be working hard to stabilize.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Hold the barbell steady as you pump your glutes.

groups.summary: Don't rush these reps. Control your tempo to max the benefits.
